    <item>
      <title>SmartStop自存储REIT在8.1亿美元IPO之后攀升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/smartstop-self-storage-reit-advances-after-810-million-us-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SmartStop Self Storage REIT Inc.在自存储房地产投资信托基金（Self Storage Real Estate Investment Trust）在首次公开募股中筹集了8.1亿美元之后，获得了市场的首次亮相，并将其股票在销售范围的下半年定价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/smartstop-self-storage-reit-advances-after-810-million-us-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 17:03:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>290亿美元激增后，Newsmax暴跌77％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/newsmax-s-value-cut-in-half-after-2-230-surge-loses-momentum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Newsmax Inc.的股票在周三的价值中占据了四分之三以上的价值，因为零售商人的一部分激增了两天的激增，使其比Fox Corp更大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/newsmax-s-value-cut-in-half-after-2-230-surge-loses-momentum</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 15:56:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普征收10％全球关税，美国股票期货跌跌撞撞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/us-stocks-slide-as-economic-worries-flare-ahead-of-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统表示，美国将开始对其全球贸易伙伴征收10％的关税，美国股票的趋势急剧下降，数十个国家面临最大的贸易失衡的国家率高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/us-stocks-slide-as-economic-worries-flare-ahead-of-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 13:50:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普宣布对中国，欧洲关税后的石油撤退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对包括中国和欧洲联盟在内的主要贸易伙伴的大量关税进行关税时，石油撤退了，这引起了人们对原油需求下降的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 23:30:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>S＆amp; p 500在较晚的特朗普关税上下降1.5％：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统概述了互惠关税之后，债券在很晚的时间内下降，债券上升，其中包括欧盟20％的征收，日本为24％，中国34％。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 22:27:39 GMT</pubDate>
